data.description: Stunning, picture-perfect home in Houma's Historic District! This New Orleans styled home has all the charm and character you're looking for. In addition to the 3 Bedrooms, 2 Full Bathrooms this house features a large dining room adjacent to the living area. A large bonus room can be used as a game room, playroom, study, library, or however else you desire. Large backyard with extra tall privacy fence allows room for a garden or play area - current garden can be removed before the AOS upon request. Many improvements / upgrades were made over the past two years to include new 50-gallon gas hot water heater, new architectural metal roof, new bathtub & shower in Primary Bathroom, new A/C unit and ventilation, new flooring in most of the house, new kitchen cabinets & backsplash, new granite kitchen countertops, new windows & hurricane shutters, and most of inside freshly painted in the last two years just to name a few. This house is only one block off of the carnival parade route. Buyer to verify all measurements and flood zone. This house should be at the top of your list when you start looking around.  It will check most, if not all, of your boxes.
